title: Havent received aniversary summ icon
body: So as time went past the deadline of the reward gifting period i havent received the summoner icon. I have received  Riot kayle  thx for that, that skin is awesome  but i wonder if i could get the icon too.

replies.body: We're still getting gifts sent out until the 30th. Most players have already gotten theirs, but if you don't have anything after the 30th passes, let me know.
